---
title: Chermoula Beef Kofta Couscous Bowl with Mint & Yoghurt Drizzle
description: Spiced beef koftas steal the show in this vibrant couscous bowl, packed with peppery radish, fragrant mint, and a cooling drizzle of creamy yoghurt. It’s a perfect mix of herby and refreshing flavours.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67d739ad6526e41d967ae48c-c5fd556c-fdf7abfe.jpeg
